Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.47,0:01:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.76,0:01:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我修的肯定沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.82,0:01:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了  是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.68,0:01:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.96,0:01:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試著回答看看
