Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.89,0:02:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樂園～開端
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.44,0:03:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真矢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.71,0:03:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.34,0:03:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社團的晨練嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.19,0:03:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說今天沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說又去羽佐間家了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.94,0:03:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.90,0:04:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天能去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能進去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天  後來被媽媽罵了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說「要是因為你害真矢遲到了怎麼辦」
