Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事用不著在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  看起來比昨天精神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.36,0:04:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.86,0:04:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要 咲良上學去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.68,0:04:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.89,0:05:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還沒好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.78,0:05:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  一定很快就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.18,0:05:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很重要的書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上回來的嗎  總士
