Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在CDC提交報告書  回來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.14,0:06:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學到不少東西吧
