Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我沒看見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城  你回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
