Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正乘坐運輸艦前往格納庫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.80,0:15:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的兒子也是法夫那的駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.79,0:15:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.23,0:15:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運輸艦在龍宮島南部250米附近失去信號
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.31,0:15:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛員及工作人員7名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生死不明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:15:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標正前往法夫那的格納庫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想搶先擊潰巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動龍宮島的ETM
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.86,0:16:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕一點點也好  拖住他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備完畢  ETM發射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標捕捉成功
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  我來駕駛法夫那
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有你要做的事  只有你才辦得到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齊格飛系統
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能行  總士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.45,0:16:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍宮島ETM還有兩分鐘至極限
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運輸艦那邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.52,0:16:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  還不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎擊繼續  升高防護壁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.34,0:17:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一分鐘也好一秒鐘也好  多堅持一下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.12,0:17:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁  明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是現階段最合適的人選
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要起用他了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.97,0:17:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們  會到哪裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.15,0:17:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ETM防護力下降
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.59,0:17:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法夫那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.39,0:17:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法夫那？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.86,0:17:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取自為了保護寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變身成龍的巨人之名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了與異界體戰鬥而開發出的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.15,0:18:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要與他們的讀心能力對抗就只能用法夫那戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑藉這個  希望你能保護這個島
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能  我不可能辦得到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.72,0:18:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  你的身體可以與法夫那一體化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.21,0:18:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要保護這個島嶼只能依靠法夫那了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.92,0:18:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的話  我很想去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.12,0:18:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在能辦得到的只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的能辦到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法夫那Mark XI 單機作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.88,0:18:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.74,0:18:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NO.11巨龍之洞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.41,0:18:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.38,0:18:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齊格飛系統準備
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士  拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.68,0:19:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.68,0:19:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑這樣的數據即使沒有作戰服也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.71,0:19:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.97,0:19:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.37,0:19:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.71,0:19:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發動尼貝龍根
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.37,0:19:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼貝龍根
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對戰數據檢測輸入
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.24,0:20:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機體行動模式認證
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼伯龍根啟動確認
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齊格飛系統接續
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法夫那發動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是第三區域
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器庫的密碼上鎖了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有聲帶解碼就無法拿到武器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那法夫那不就是赤手空拳了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.98,0:20:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁  接下來拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎  一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士  你為什麼在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是通過腦波和你直接交流的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在法夫那里的你和在齊格飛中的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.62,0:21:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大腦皮層的細胞是直接相連的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.00,0:21:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有作戰服不能完全同步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.08,0:21:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在優先考慮與法夫那一體化的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.92,0:21:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先睜開眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.24,0:21:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睜開眼睛？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.23,0:21:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  法夫那的眼睛就是你的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.08,0:21:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.37,0:21:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  他來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開啟NO.11巨龍之洞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.31,0:21:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法夫那Mark XI 出發
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.70,0:21:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們旅途的開端
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.47,0:21:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們能活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.22,0:21:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要忘記迄今為止的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.94,0:21:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天要讓這個島嶼變回樂園
